---
title: Cheesy Homestyle Fish & Bacon Pie with Filo Pastry & Apple Salad
description: Who doesn’t love a pie? We know we do, and we know you’ll love this one too. Tender hoki is gently cooked and stirred through a cheesy, veggie-packed filling. Flavoured with Dijon mustard and encased in golden, flaky filo, this pie is sure to be a hit!
